journals.notes:
In GXP's CSS files I replaced: 
@http://extjs.cachefly.net/ext-3.4.0/@
by
@../../ext/@


For example:
@background-image:url(http://extjs.cachefly.net/ext-3.4.0/resources/images/gray/panel/tool-sprites.gif);@
becomes:
@background-image:url(../../ext/resources/images/gray/panel/tool-sprites.gif);@
